 "claim_id": 1,
 "text": "The Oregon Death with Dignity Act (1997) and the Swiss assisted‑suicide framework demonstrate that legal assisted suicide with strict criteria does not increase overall suicide rates and is associated with reduced suffering.",
 "type": "empirical"
 },
